# repo — plugins/session-atlas/scripts/session-atlas — generalized (multi-account,
# publish, gists, refresh endpoint all via ~/.config/session-atlas/config.json)
# and shipped as the `session-atlas` plugin in the blackbox-ai-labs marketplace.
#
# The desktop launcher ~/.local/bin/claude-session-atlas snapshots the engine
# from THAT repo's origin/main; the systemd user units (timer + refresh socket)
